 We put six drops of
lavender on this pad here.

00:00:15.610 --> 00:00:19.120
And then we just turn it on.

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:22.490
And then there's a little heater
in here, an electric heater,

00:00:22.490 --> 00:00:24.800
